The spectrum of vascular involvement in giant-cell arteritis: clinical 
consequences of detrimental vascular remodelling at different sites.

Cid MC(1), Prieto-González S, Arguis P, Espígol-Frigolé G, Butjosa M, 
Hernández-Rodríguez J, Segarra M, Lozano E, García-Martínez A.

